						<li><a class="icons icon-icons_email-top-share tagmanager" title="Share by Email" href="mailto:?subject=Sharing a story from Hakai Magazine&body=I thought you might find this story interesting:%0D%0A%0D%0ASeabirds Can Help Predict the Size of Fish Stocks—If Only We’d Listen%0D%0AThe scientists who study terns, puffins, and other fish-eating birds are trying to get fisheries managers to heed their warnings.%0D%0Ahttps://hakaimagazine.com/news/seabirds-can-predict-the-size-of-fish-stocks-if-only-wed-listen/" target="_blank"><span>Share by Email</span></a></li>



					</ul>
